data.text:
French Marshal King of Naples Grand Duke of Berg 1767-1815

This is a historical miniature of Marshal Joachim Murat 54 mm , scale 1/32. The Marshal of France and Grand Admiral or Admiral of France, was Grand Duke of Berg from 1806 to 1808 and then King of Naples from 1808 to 1815. He received his titles in part by being the brother-in-law of Napoleon Bonaparte, through marriage to Napoleon's youngest sister, Caroline Bonaparte.
